{"word":"G5105 - τοιγαροῦν - toigaroûn - toy-gar-oon' - There-fore","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τοιγαροῦν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">toigaroûn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">toy-gar-oon'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">There-fore</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆகையால் - அனுமான பிற்சேர்க்கை"},{"paragraph":"wherefore then, for which reason, therefore, consequently"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5104 - τοί - toí - toy/5104\">G5104</a> and <a href=\"#/G1063 - γάρ - gár - gar/1063\">G1063</a> and <a href=\"#/G3767 - οὖν - oûn - oon/3767\">G3767</a>; <i>truly for then</i>, that is, <i>consequently:</i> - there- (where-) fore.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}